description: tokyocabinet aims to be a complete python wrapper for the          Tokyo Cabinet database library by Mikio Hirabayashi (http178th.net).                  So far the btree, hash and table APIs have been fully wrapped.
longdescription: tokyocabinet aims to be a complete python wrapper for the          Tokyo Cabinet database library by Mikio Hirabayashi (http178th.net).                  So far the btree, hash and table APIs have been fully wrapped.
